  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Primitive Variables (often referred as &quot;primvars&quot;) are data attached to the geometry.  This is useful when a shader needs to reference custom data from the geometry. There is no need to remap Houdini primvars to RenderMan primvars. All geometry attributes are passed to RenderMan as primvars with specific variation depending on attribute type. </p><p>The examples below show the difference between the four Houdini attribute types (point, vertex, uniform, detail) and how they translate to RenderMan primvars. All the Houdini attributes regardless of type are all RenderMan primvars so can be accessed via the PxrPrimvar VOP. </p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/pxrprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=490&amp;height=163\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/pxrprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"163\" data-width=\"490\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643778\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrprimvar.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a26555d5-29e4-41e0-baac-2f42b51cdf28\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/pxrprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=490&amp;height=163 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/pxrprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=490&amp;height=163 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"point.PNG\" width=\"297\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/point.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=295\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/point.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"385\" data-width=\"386\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643775\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"point.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3b4224b3-1b0b-41f2-bbdc-a705792ea7d4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/point.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=515&amp;height=513 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/point.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=295 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"vertex.PNG\" width=\"297\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/vertex.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=295\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/vertex.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"386\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643772\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"vertex.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f8ab1495-c154-424a-8dae-333048cffa3b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/vertex.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=514&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/vertex.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=295 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"prim.PNG\" width=\"297\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/prim.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=290\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/prim.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"383\" data-width=\"392\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643769\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"prim.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"90fd9c6b-800e-4638-a405-84290dac7051\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/prim.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=510 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/prim.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=290 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"detail.PNG\" width=\"297\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/detail.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=292\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/detail.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"390\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643766\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"detail.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"022b4b41-202d-48bc-96a1-130e9f337eb3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/detail.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=520&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/detail.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118651&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=297&amp;height=292 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><p>Houdini attributes can also be used to control aspects of rendering such as shading, dicing, displacement, or geometry specific settings by creating <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662093/Primitive+Variables\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662093\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">primitive variables</a> that are recognized by RenderMan. These can be set via a houdini detail attribute in SOPs or by adding RenderMan spare parameters to the OBJ. If both parameter and attribute are set, the detail attribute will override the OBJ parameter.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"141\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/detailattr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=141\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/detailattr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643781\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"detailattr.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"38363610-2d80-4ea2-88c1-4c6dab29f1b1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/detailattr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=141 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/detailattr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433118869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=141 1x\"></span> <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"138\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/objprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119034&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=138\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/objprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119034&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643784\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"objprimvar.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ba697d33-0471-4ab2-9e46-97058424f5c8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/objprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119034&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=138 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/objprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119034&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=138 1x\"></span></p><p /><p class=\"media-group\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper conf-macro output-inline\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-macro-id=\"cc8d523c-3f14-4093-9cad-674589781ea9\" data-macro-name=\"view-file\"><a class=\"confluence-embedded-file\" href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/primvars.hip?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119034&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-nice-type=\"null\" data-file-src=\"/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/primvars.hip?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119034&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643787\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"primvars.hip\" data-mime-type=\"application/octet-stream\" data-has-thumbnail=\"true\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"906ef396-46d5-4b8d-a555-3957c754d6a8\" data-media-type=\"file\"><img src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/primvars.hip?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119034&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;viewType=fileMacro\" height=\"250\" /></a></span></p><p /><hr/><p /><p><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661983/Instance+Attributes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661983\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Instance Attributes</a> are data attached to the instance. This useful for varying attributes across instances. Like primvars, instance attributes can also be added via SOP attributes or via OBJ parameters.  </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/attribute.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=148\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643750/attribute.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"148\" data-width=\"565\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643802\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"attribute.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643750\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"179b28a6-2c56-4e85-9572-324bd6437d70\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/attribute.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=148 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/attribute.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433119358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=148 1x\"></span><p /><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"center\" data-local-id=\"04e463bd-9d56-4d41-8c52-4ad368423d86\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>via SOPs</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>via OBJs</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>user</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"374\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643750/color.PNG?version=1&amp;modific